      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s been really well-loved, you\u2019ve found it! This beauty runs like a dream and is ready for all your upcoming road trips. It\u2019s in great shape and has been kept clean and tidy. I'm sad to see it go, but it's time for its next adventure with a new owner. Feel free to shoot me a message\u2014I'd love to chat and get you behind the wheel!",
