    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of a well-maintained daily driver, offering a perfect balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a brilliant shine, showing only minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with responsible use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the upholstery is supple with no tears, and the dashboard remains free of any sun damage or cracking. Every feature, including the premium audio system, navigation, and heated seats, has been tested and works perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with a consistent idle, backed by a complete history of on-time oil changes and scheduled maintenance. We recently fitted a new set of high-performance all-season tires and performed a full brake service, ensuring the car is ready for the road the moment you take the keys. It drives straight, shifts crisply, and offers a quiet, composed ride. Documentation of all recent work is included for your peace of mind.",
